captions.text: Let's play "Improbable Version"!

Everybody plays. We're
gonna tell you a child's story,

in an improbable version.
Each player has a character

and we will switch through
them as I ring the bell.

The producers gave us some
characters in this envelope...

Daniel is someone who just
hit his pinky toe in a corner!

Andy will be in a reality show
elimination day.

Edu will be
São Paulo's mayor Maluf!

And Elidio will talk like
he was in a western!

All right? Who in the audience
can suggest a child's story?

There.
What's your suggestion?

- Three Little Pigs!
- Three Little Pigs is nice.

Elidio will start. "Improbable Version",
'Three Little Pigs', starting now!
In a pigsty very far away...

Were there was
no longer a damn thing...
Daniel!
Edu!

The pig went to get straw in the
program Straw For The People.
So he could build his socialized house.

- Because in my government...
- Elidio!

And the town was almost empty,
just a straw house...

A stick house... A brick house...
And the wolf.
Andy!
It's not that I don't like the wolf...
It's an affinity thing, Julie!
Daniel!
Just a moment...
Edu!

Mister wolf, if you catch the pig,
rape him, but don't kill him!
Andy!

I just wanna say that
the pigs are playing their game.

I'm just trying to survive...
Yeah, I'm playing my game.
Yeah, I'm huffing and puffing!
Daniel!
Elidio!

The straw house was blown to hell,
and the pig ran and ran...

He ran like a horse
on a competition day...
Andy!

It looks like the little pig was saved
by you, POV pig number two!
Daniel!
There were three little pigs...
Edu!

But they got away by the
Imigrantes Road, which I built!
And they kept going...

And I didn't even mention
the Ostensive Patrol...

- What is the pig's political party, Maluf?
- It's PPP. The Pig's Progressive Party!

CIA. BARBIXAS DE HUMOR
presented

IMPROVÁVEL
Probably a good show.
